name: Strength of Faith Necklace
description:
This necklace makes a bold, yet tasteful statement of faith. Wood beads, natural and dark brown, are accented with silver finish spacer and garnet Czech fire polished crystals. The cross pendant is of silver finish base metal, like the clasp.

	Strength of Faith was made to be a unisex necklace; either men or women can wear this necklace proudly.

	All jewelry is shipped in well-padded packaging to ensure safe delivery of your products. Gift wrap is also available; please request in the special instructions field.

name: Love in Black Phone Charm
description: Sleek in design, this is a 3” phone charm that has a classic simplicity. Black seed beads are accented with silvertone and moonstone shades. A charm with a thorny heart on one side and the word “love” on the other says it all.

name: January Companion Rosary
description:
A companion rosary is a full, five-decade pocket rosary in miniature. They each are different, and have a beautiful personality all their own.

	Length: 7 inches
HM Beads: Coral Red Seed Beads
OF Beads: Garnet Czech Firepolished Crystal
Centerpiece: Red Glass Teardrop
Cross/Crucifix: Silver finish base metal crucifix (.75”)

	This tiny rosary comes with an “instruction book” for praying the rosary.
